00:10:29.440 --> 00:10:31.110
I'm trying to encourage you all to

00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:32.990
know that God's going to take care

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:35.990
of you. Believing for a creative

00:10:35.990 --> 00:10:36.000
idea—I

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:38.310
know a lot of people don't want

00:10:38.320 --> 00:10:39.949
to hear this, but there's a lot of people

00:10:39.959 --> 00:10:41.350
that are struggling because we get the

00:10:41.360 --> 00:10:45.710
emails, and I know that God is a provider.

00:10:45.720 --> 00:10:49.069
God is El Elyon, the Most High.

00:10:49.079 --> 00:10:51.629
He is a Jehovah Jireh. He will provide for

00:10:51.639 --> 00:10:54.190
you, he will heal you, he will deliver you,

00:10:54.200 --> 00:10:55.949
and all you have to do is reach out

00:10:55.959 --> 00:10:59.470
in simple faith.

00:10:59.470 --> 00:10:59.480
Abraham—it

00:10:59.480 --> 00:11:01.710
says in the word—Abraham staggered not

00:11:01.720 --> 00:11:04.470
at the promise of God through unbelief.

00:11:04.480 --> 00:11:06.790
He knew in the deadness of her womb, she

00:11:06.800 --> 00:11:07.910
was

00:11:07.920 --> 00:11:11.110
old, there was no life in

00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:13.750
that womb to bring forth a

00:11:13.760 --> 00:11:18.110
new child, but the Lord saw to it to

00:11:18.120 --> 00:11:21.350
bring him forth, Isaac. And I believe with

00:11:21.360 --> 00:11:24.069
all my heart that there's Isaacs coming,

00:11:24.079 --> 00:11:26.990
not just in babies, but in every area

00:11:27.000 --> 00:11:29.829
of your life.

00:11:29.829 --> 00:11:29.839
Isaacs—there's

00:11:29.839 --> 00:11:31.350
blessings, there's

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:33.389
increase, there's new jobs, there's

00:11:33.399 --> 00:11:34.949
multiplication, there's

00:11:34.959 --> 00:11:37.629
promotions. Whatever you may need, I

00:11:37.639 --> 00:11:39.829
believe with all my heart God has your

00:11:39.839 --> 00:11:41.829
Isaac. Does that make sense what I'm

00:11:41.839 --> 00:11:43.030
trying to say, ladies and gentlemen? I'm

00:11:43.040 --> 00:11:45.470
trying to tell you to believe God

00:11:45.480 --> 00:11:48.870
and stagger not at the promises that God

00:11:48.880 --> 00:11:51.350
said he would supply for all your needs

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:52.870
according to riches and glory, that he

00:11:52.880 --> 00:11:54.509
would heal you by his stripes, that he

00:11:54.519 --> 00:11:56.190
would deliver you, and that with long

00:11:56.200 --> 00:11:58.269
life he would satisfy you and show you

00:11:58.279 --> 00:12:00.670
his salvation—Psalms 91—and that he would

00:12:00.680 --> 00:12:02.949
give you peace in your homes. You

00:12:02.959 --> 00:12:05.069
don't have to go home tonight and be

00:12:05.079 --> 00:12:06.910
tormented and go, 'Well, you know, we're

00:12:06.920 --> 00:12:08.430
going to go home, my wife and I are going

00:12:08.440 --> 00:12:10.550
to fight probably all night and I'll

00:12:10.560 --> 00:12:12.269
sleep in the other room, won't have

00:12:12.279 --> 00:12:14.590
anybody to be with because

00:12:14.600 --> 00:12:16.949
our marriage is just

00:12:16.959 --> 00:12:20.670
terrible.'Remember,

00:12:20.680 --> 00:12:23.030
you have what you say. The Bible

00:12:23.040 --> 00:12:24.949
says call those things that be not as

00:12:24.959 --> 00:12:27.150
though they were, and you have to speak

00:12:27.160 --> 00:12:29.350
to your circumstances and say, 'My

00:12:29.360 --> 00:12:31.670
marriage is good.'Even whenever Diana and

00:12:31.680 --> 00:12:32.990
I were having a hard time when Megan was

00:12:33.000 --> 00:12:35.990
first diagnosed, there were days, because of

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:37.590
how much pressure it was having a

00:12:37.600 --> 00:12:39.829
special needs child, that I was like, 'Man,

00:12:39.839 --> 00:12:41.750
I don't want to do this

00:12:41.750 --> 00:12:41.760
anymore.'It

00:12:41.760 --> 00:12:43.269
wasn't because of Diana; it was because

00:12:43.279 --> 00:12:45.310
the circumstances were

00:12:45.310 --> 00:12:45.320
making—I've

00:12:45.320 --> 00:12:47.189
always loved Diana, we've had a really

00:12:47.199 --> 00:12:48.910
good friendship and a good marriage, but

00:12:48.920 --> 00:12:50.710
there's been times whenever there's been

00:12:50.720 --> 00:12:53.949
pressure from circumstances of life

00:12:53.959 --> 00:12:55.550
that really try to put pressure on the

00:12:55.560 --> 00:12:57.069
marriage and put pressure on the

00:12:57.079 --> 00:12:59.230
finances, pressure on things that you go,

00:12:59.240 --> 00:13:00.829
'I don't want to do this anymore.'And

00:13:00.829 --> 00:13:00.839
you've

00:13:00.839 --> 00:13:02.990
got to have that

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:06.189
inside, that bulldog on a bone, saying, 'I

00:13:06.199 --> 00:13:08.910
will keep doing this. I signed up for

00:13:08.920 --> 00:13:10.430
this, I'm going to do this. I made a

00:13:10.440 --> 00:13:11.990
covenant with her, I made a covenant with

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:13.910
him, and we're going to walk through the

00:13:13.920 --> 00:13:15.750
valley and we're going to make this

00:13:15.760 --> 00:13:18.430
happen. We're not quitters, we're fighters,

00:13:18.440 --> 00:13:20.710
and we're doers of the word,

00:13:20.720 --> 00:13:23.150
regardless of how hard life throws these curveballs

00:13:23.150 --> 00:13:23.160
and fastballs

00:13:23.160 --> 00:13:26.189
at

00:13:26.189 --> 00:13:26.199
you.'You've

00:13:26.199 --> 00:13:28.870
got to keep on keeping on and

00:13:28.870 --> 00:13:28.880
know

00:13:28.880 --> 00:13:32.110
that we're not quitters. We have to be

00:13:32.120 --> 00:13:33.870
the army, and we have to be

00:13:33.880 --> 00:13:36.430
the backbone. And when

00:13:36.440 --> 00:13:38.230
things are thrown at us the

00:13:38.240 --> 00:13:40.030
hardest, that's whenever you keep saying

00:13:40.040 --> 00:13:42.790
the strongest, 'Nope, I'm

00:13:42.800 --> 00:13:44.350
going to keep making this marriage work.

00:13:44.360 --> 00:13:45.710
Nope, I'm going to fight and I'm going to

00:13:45.720 --> 00:13:47.150
believe for my child's

00:13:47.160 --> 00:13:49.069
healing. No, I'm going to believe for a

00:13:49.079 --> 00:13:51.350
better job, I'm going to believe God for

00:13:51.360 --> 00:13:53.990
a creative idea.'And it didn't even come

00:13:54.000 --> 00:13:56.110
through me, ladies and gentlemen. The idea

00:13:56.120 --> 00:13:58.749
to do eBay, the idea to do Poshmark,

00:13:58.749 --> 00:13:58.759
the

00:13:58.759 --> 00:14:02.069
ideas to sell things on

00:14:02.079 --> 00:14:05.069
Facebook Marketplace—that came from

00:14:05.079 --> 00:14:08.310
the Holy Spirit and my wife. So you think

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:09.629
a lot of times, 'Well, it's going

00:14:09.639 --> 00:14:11.990
to have to come through the

00:14:11.990 --> 00:14:12.000
man.'No,

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:13.829
listen to your wife and what she has to say.

00:14:13.839 --> 00:14:15.710
She may have a creative idea that might

00:14:15.720 --> 00:14:17.870
get you out of the hole, too. Don't always

00:14:17.880 --> 00:14:19.670
try to be the one who says, 'Well, I'm the head, I'm

00:14:19.680 --> 00:14:20.790
going to get this

00:14:20.790 --> 00:14:20.800
through.'No,

00:14:20.800 --> 00:14:23.829
it came through my

00:14:23.829 --> 00:14:23.839
sweet

00:14:23.839 --> 00:14:26.389
wife, and whenever she said it, I didn't even

00:14:26.399 --> 00:14:29.110
believe it. I'd say, 'Is this the way God

00:14:29.120 --> 00:14:31.189
wants to do this for our

00:14:31.189 --> 00:14:31.199
family?'because

00:14:31.199 --> 00:14:32.790
pride comes in as a

00:14:32.800 --> 00:14:34.389
man and you think, 'Well, I'm not going to

00:14:34.399 --> 00:14:37.430
listen to that.'And I just

00:14:37.440 --> 00:14:39.870
had to just say, 'Listen, buddy,

00:14:39.880 --> 00:14:41.430
you better shut your

00:14:41.430 --> 00:14:41.440
mouth.'You

00:14:41.440 --> 00:14:43.670
know what I'm saying?

00:14:43.680 --> 00:14:46.269
I'm just saying,

00:14:46.279 --> 00:14:48.269
there is a lot of times that the Lord

00:14:48.279 --> 00:14:52.269
will use unexpected ways, and it doesn't

00:14:52.279 --> 00:14:55.550
have to be how you think

00:14:55.560 --> 00:14:57.910
it's going to happen

00:14:57.910 --> 00:14:57.920
because

00:14:57.920 --> 00:14:59.870
you try to box

00:14:59.880 --> 00:15:02.269
God in, you try to limit God, you try to

00:15:02.279 --> 00:15:03.230
tell him, 'This is how you're going to

00:15:03.240 --> 00:15:05.550
operate in our life.'And God

00:15:05.550 --> 00:15:05.560
is

00:15:05.560 --> 00:15:07.189
exceedingly abundantly above all that

00:15:07.199 --> 00:15:08.949
you dare ask or think.

00:15:08.959 --> 00:15:10.509
God is not going to operate in

00:15:10.519 --> 00:15:12.590
your peanut brain in how he's going to

00:15:12.600 --> 00:15:14.990
get it to you. It comes through—like I

00:15:15.000 --> 00:15:16.910
told you all, I had a man—I was

00:15:16.920 --> 00:15:19.030
just cleaning the floors of the church,

00:15:19.040 --> 00:15:21.030
not expecting it at all. It was a big

00:15:21.040 --> 00:15:23.030
Christmas program that we were doing

00:15:23.040 --> 00:15:24.910
at the church and I was just in there

00:15:24.920 --> 00:15:26.230
cleaning, and we didn't have any

00:15:26.240 --> 00:15:27.629
Christmas presents for the kids or

00:15:27.639 --> 00:15:29.350
anything. We wanted to get the gifts for

00:15:29.360 --> 00:15:31.910
the family and we were like, 'Man,

00:15:31.910 --> 00:15:31.920
Lord,'and

00:15:31.920 --> 00:15:33.829
we were down to nothing. And this man

00:15:33.839 --> 00:15:37.069
out of nowhere walks up to

00:15:37.069 --> 00:15:37.079
me—his

00:15:37.079 --> 00:15:39.470
name was Tim—and he walked up to me

00:15:39.480 --> 00:15:42.030
and he said, 'The Lord told me to give you

00:15:42.040 --> 00:15:43.550
this

00:15:43.550 --> 00:15:43.560
$1,000.'It

00:15:43.560 --> 00:15:46.110
would have

00:15:46.120 --> 00:15:47.710
seemed like it was a million dollars,

00:15:47.720 --> 00:15:49.509
ladies and gentlemen, for where we were.

00:15:49.509 --> 00:15:49.519
$1,000—that

00:15:49.519 --> 00:15:53.470
was like—because I only made

00:15:53.480 --> 00:15:55.910
like eight bucks an hour. So when you

00:15:55.920 --> 00:15:57.670
get

00:15:57.680 --> 00:16:02.670
$1,000 on janitor's wages, you go, 'My

00:16:02.670 --> 00:16:02.680
God.'You

00:16:02.680 --> 00:16:05.829
know, the Lord came through. And I

00:16:05.839 --> 00:16:07.430
remember sitting there when he walked

00:16:07.440 --> 00:16:10.189
away, I went outside and I called Diana

00:16:10.199 --> 00:16:13.150
and I said, 'Babe, the Lord just provided

00:16:13.160 --> 00:16:13.990
our

00:16:13.990 --> 00:16:14.000
Christmas,'and

00:16:14.000 --> 00:16:16.910
she just wept on the

00:16:16.920 --> 00:16:20.030
phone with me. We both wept because God

00:16:20.040 --> 00:16:22.110
came through. And it's not just one time

00:16:22.120 --> 00:16:24.910
he's done that. If he did it once, he'll

00:16:24.920 --> 00:16:27.189
do it again. And that's where we believe

00:16:27.199 --> 00:16:29.230
him all the time, even today for it,

00:16:29.240 --> 00:16:30.590
ladies and gentlemen. I don't always have

00:16:30.600 --> 00:16:33.150
my stuff together. I may—you may think I

00:16:33.160 --> 00:16:35.110
do, and it may seem like I do on this

00:16:35.120 --> 00:16:37.230
camera, but we believe God for stuff all

00:16:37.240 --> 00:16:39.430
the time. We're still believing him for

00:16:39.440 --> 00:16:41.629
stuff. You say, 'Well, Brandon, what are you

00:16:41.639 --> 00:16:42.910
doing with your faith right

00:16:42.910 --> 00:16:42.920
now?'I'm

00:16:42.920 --> 00:16:45.309
believing for things that if I told you

00:16:45.319 --> 00:16:47.629
what I was believing for, it would freak

00:16:47.639 --> 00:16:49.829
you out because of things the Lord has

00:16:49.839 --> 00:16:51.829
told me that we're going to have to do

00:16:51.839 --> 00:16:54.990
for this ministry. But we keep on, and we

00:16:55.000 --> 00:16:57.470
know that it is not by our might, not

00:16:57.480 --> 00:16:59.230
by my power, but by the spirit,

00:16:59.240 --> 00:17:02.230
says the Lord. Regardless of how big it

00:17:02.240 --> 00:17:03.870
is, sometimes

00:17:03.880 --> 00:17:06.189
the mountain seems so big that you can't

00:17:06.199 --> 00:17:09.150
climb it and you go, 'How in the world am

00:17:09.160 --> 00:17:11.029
I going to get up there?'other than just

00:17:11.039 --> 00:17:14.510
say, 'Lord, I trust you. You said it, and now

00:17:14.520 --> 00:17:16.590
you're going to bring it to pass. You

00:17:16.600 --> 00:17:18.590
told us to do it, now you're going to

00:17:18.600 --> 00:17:20.429
bring it to pass. I'm not going to be

00:17:20.439 --> 00:17:22.590
moved by what I see. I'm not moved by

00:17:22.600 --> 00:17:25.029
what I feel.'If you don't bring it,

00:17:25.039 --> 00:17:26.829
I'm not going to worry about it.

00:17:29.760 --> 00:17:32.390
It's your bill,

00:17:32.400 --> 00:17:34.830
Lord.

00:17:40.960 --> 00:17:43.510
I used to get so upset about it, I

00:17:43.520 --> 00:17:45.590
used to have anxiety about it, and it was

00:17:45.600 --> 00:17:48.190
bad. For a long time, I told Die, I said,

00:17:48.200 --> 00:17:50.029
'If I could just get a couple

00:17:50.039 --> 00:17:51.990
months extra in the bank

00:17:52.000 --> 00:17:53.470
so I don't stress out about these

00:17:53.480 --> 00:17:55.510
finances all the time—about your

00:17:55.520 --> 00:17:57.310
electric, your water, your gas, and your

00:17:57.320 --> 00:17:59.390
car payment.'Because there was a time whenever

00:17:59.400 --> 00:18:01.390
they repoed our car; they came

00:18:01.400 --> 00:18:03.070
and took it, and we would sit there and

00:18:03.080 --> 00:18:04.909
just watch it go down the street. It

00:18:04.909 --> 00:18:04.919
sucks—it's

00:18:04.919 --> 00:18:07.789
just

00:18:07.799 --> 00:18:10.630
being real. And you get to that

00:18:10.640 --> 00:18:11.950
point where

00:18:11.960 --> 00:18:14.590
you get really discouraged when

00:18:14.600 --> 00:18:16.750
they come and get your broke-down Honda

00:18:16.760 --> 00:18:20.350
with 200,000 miles on it, and you're

00:18:20.360 --> 00:18:23.190
going, 'What gives?'And then

00:18:23.200 --> 00:18:24.230
you keep believing. That's what I'm

00:18:24.240 --> 00:18:25.950
trying to tell y'all. We've been there. We

00:18:25.960 --> 00:18:27.510
know what it's like to be at the bottom

00:18:27.520 --> 00:18:28.870
of the barrel and the barrel be on

00:18:28.880 --> 00:18:32.110
top of you, like Brother Hagin used to

00:18:32.120 --> 00:18:36.950
say. But God, who is rich in mercy. So I

00:18:36.960 --> 00:18:40.149
hope this encourages you today that

00:18:40.159 --> 00:18:42.310
you're not alone. You may think

00:18:42.320 --> 00:18:43.909
you're alone, you may think God's not

00:18:43.919 --> 00:18:46.149
hearing you, you may think

00:18:46.159 --> 00:18:48.630
he's abandoned

00:18:48.640 --> 00:18:50.710
us, 'We don't even have enough

00:18:50.720 --> 00:18:52.870
for some Spam and some peanut butter and

00:18:52.870 --> 00:18:52.880
jelly.'But

00:18:52.880 --> 00:18:55.789
I'm telling you, if

00:18:55.799 --> 00:18:57.710
you keep on being faithful, you keep

00:18:57.720 --> 00:18:59.590
speaking to your circumstances, if you

00:18:59.600 --> 00:19:01.190
keep calling those things that be not as

00:19:01.200 --> 00:19:02.870
though they were, you keep speaking to

00:19:02.880 --> 00:19:04.990
your marriage—'My marriage is good, my

00:19:05.000 --> 00:19:07.149
marriage is whole, my marriage is

00:19:07.149 --> 00:19:07.159
healthy'—because

00:19:07.159 --> 00:19:08.830
what you say out of your mouth is

00:19:08.840 --> 00:19:10.710
what you're going to have tomorrow. What

00:19:10.720 --> 00:19:12.310
you said out of your mouth today is what

00:19:12.320 --> 00:19:14.510
you lived

00:19:14.520 --> 00:19:17.870
yesterday. Life is a series of choices. We

00:19:17.880 --> 00:19:20.750
were talking about it even yesterday; I

00:19:20.760 --> 00:19:22.510
said, 'Isn't it amazing, it's the

00:19:22.520 --> 00:19:24.789
small decisions that make the big

00:19:24.789 --> 00:19:24.799
decision.'We're

00:19:24.799 --> 00:19:26.950
always looking for the

00:19:26.960 --> 00:19:30.390
big thing. For

00:19:30.390 --> 00:19:30.400
me,

00:19:30.400 --> 00:19:32.310
struggling with my weight, eating wrong

00:19:32.320 --> 00:19:34.669
foods, bad foods during the

00:19:34.669 --> 00:19:34.679
day—I'll

00:19:34.679 --> 00:19:36.149
pick up something and put it in my mouth, it's

00:19:36.159 --> 00:19:38.470
something so small and yet it tries to

00:19:38.480 --> 00:19:40.950
ruin me. It's something that I deal with,

00:19:40.960 --> 00:19:43.470
and you get that

00:19:43.480 --> 00:19:45.149
stress and you go, 'Man, I've got to have

00:19:45.159 --> 00:19:46.549
that piece of candy,'and I put it in my

00:19:46.559 --> 00:19:48.470
mouth and I didn't even realize I did it

00:19:48.480 --> 00:19:50.149
because it's just something

00:19:50.159 --> 00:19:51.750
that I've dealt

00:19:51.760 --> 00:19:54.590
with. And I try so hard to turn it around.

00:19:54.600 --> 00:19:56.669
I say, 'Tomorrow, the diet starts tomorrow.

00:19:56.679 --> 00:19:58.470
Tomorrow I'm going to do

00:19:58.470 --> 00:19:58.480
good.'And

00:19:58.480 --> 00:20:00.230
then you end up

00:20:00.240 --> 00:20:01.950
catching yourself with that

00:20:01.960 --> 00:20:04.390
cookie from Paisley, my little girl.

00:20:04.400 --> 00:20:06.950
She'll have a cookie and I go, 'Oh,

00:20:06.960 --> 00:20:10.070
it's

00:20:10.070 --> 00:20:10.080
gluten-free.'I

00:20:10.080 --> 00:20:12.710
just try to be real with y'all.

00:20:12.720 --> 00:20:14.590
Like I said, we all have our stuff

00:20:14.600 --> 00:20:17.950
we're going through, and none of us

00:20:17.960 --> 00:20:21.110
are perfect. We're all work in progress.

00:20:21.120 --> 00:20:22.830
But Jesus loves every single one of us

00:20:22.840 --> 00:20:24.950
where we are and he wants us to come up

00:20:24.960 --> 00:20:27.430
higher. He always—there's that gentle,

00:20:27.440 --> 00:20:30.350
still, small voice tugging

00:20:30.350 --> 00:20:30.360
at

00:20:30.360 --> 00:20:33.510
your heart. 'Brandon, you can make it, you

00:20:33.520 --> 00:20:36.390
can do this, you can make your marriage

00:20:36.400 --> 00:20:38.950
work. You can do

00:20:38.960 --> 00:20:41.070
whatever you set your mind to

00:20:41.080 --> 00:20:43.070
with the Holy Spirit.'You can achieve it.

